Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That day, I woke up from a nightmare very unpleasantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was likely a premonition signaling\Nsomething terrible was to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.49,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:20.75,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Tokomae Sayuri (40)\NClient
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:20.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, pretty please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:24.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If you're so afraid of getting robbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:28.42,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You could just leave your expensive\Naccessories at home before going out...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I want everyone to see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, just an hour a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jog with me as part of my weight-loss program!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:41.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said her deceased husband looked just like Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, being a bodyguard...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not part of detective work!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's totally into Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Join me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Mouri Detective Agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Gamou Ryouzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to find a witness who can confirm my alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, now this is what I'm talking about—some real detective work!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, tomorrow at 7:00 in the evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,General Pufferfish\NMeeting at "Fugu-Taishou" right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll talk about it more then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so sorry, Tokomae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, but\NI've suddenly had a request come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I came first!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She doesn't need a bodyguard...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, something terrible has happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is eternal, labyrinths are mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A wrong deduction leads to tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the end for Detective Kogoro!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's running late because something came up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} called and said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As an apology, he wanted you to enjoy those first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pufferfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir, a visitor for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything, Gamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:16.31,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(290,0)}Gamou Ryouzou (70)\NFinance Company Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.52,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My apologies for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.31,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I am Gamou Ryouzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I know of the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:28.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About half a month ago, at an antique store in Tsukimi City...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner, Kinugasa Sakae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was killed by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police suspected that I was the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said I had a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five years ago, I was scammed out of a large amount of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when the detectives came to check my alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but answer that I was at home on the day of murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, in actuality...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in Akebono City hanging out here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was alone and there were no witnesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought if I said I went out they would\Nsuspect me, so I couldn't help but lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they expose my lies, I bet the police will\Nsuspect me and make me the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the day of the murder, in Akebono city, I know\Nthis person saw me there —\hplease find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A search for your alibi witness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so reliable, just like they all say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I go out often and don't carry a cellphone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll personally call you when I need your results.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, eat, drink and be merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, thanks for the meal the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, you're a popular guy, Gamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we go to another bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To our hearts' content!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I started investigating first thing the next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the investigation didn't go as smoothly as expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I've been getting calls from Gamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, on the sixth day—Friday night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find something, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okino Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s on TV starting at 8:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet it's a love call from that lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Gamou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been working on it all of today as well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still couldn't find my witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I could trust a famous detective like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now, I've lost hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's he mean by "I've lost hope"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a drama-king.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time of death was estimated to be from 7:00 to 9:00 last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In addition, there's no indication of the body being moved post-death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure, I've fetched Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although it appears to be a suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found this tightly crushed piece of paper near his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My office phone number is on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please allow me a look at the face of the deceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when he told you, "I've lost hope" over the phone last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's come to confirm the identity of the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:17.26,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Arai Kyousuke (42)\NGamou's Nephew
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:17.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This is Gamou-shi's nephew, Arai Kyousuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With "I've lost hope."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We finally understand Gamou-shi's actions from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one suspected of murdering antique\Nmerchant Kinugasa Sakai, Gamou-shi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Called Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} last night at eight o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After realizing the investigation had grown\Nfutile, Gamou-shi lost hope, got in his car...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And came here to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From Gamou's house to here takes around an hour by car...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which puts his suicide at 9:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That matches our estimate as to the time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was actually innocent...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't have lost all hope just because\Nhis alibi witness couldn't be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:09.77,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Hisamoto Kango (50)\NJousai Police Department Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:09.77,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Gamou-shi had experienced the pain of\Nbeing arrested despite being innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A false arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case occurred five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinugasa Sakae, who died recently,\Nwas attacked from behind by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing witness testimony, we detectives\Nfrom the Jousai police arrested Gamou-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, a few days later, we learned of Gamou-shi's alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Being made the culprit by the police; it was really frightening."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what my uncle told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he thought he was going through that traumatic\Nordeal all over again, felt helpless, and lost all hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We vowed to investigate more thoroughly this time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't want to repeat Takeoka's failure again, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Takeoka"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mean Takeoka Isao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He felt the false arrest was his responsibility\Nand decided to leave his job with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Takeoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, he would come to visit Dad's place on occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's Takeoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}—your colleague\Nfrom way back in the police academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one suspected of murdering Kinugasa-shi is now in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll report back once I've obtained more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only they could have arrested the suspect earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle wouldn't have jumped to such conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is gonna be scary after dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any lights around, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be pitch dark around here at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be why we also found a flashlight near Gamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why did he take the trouble to prepare\Nthat in order to come here to commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could've done it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe there must've been a reason Gamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} needed to die here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One that was planned by his murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "murderer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, this is a homicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Homicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In my final phone call with Gamou-shi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said the words: "I've lost hope."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's precisely that that was used by the murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to make us believe this was a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for you to come here and do all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still—we cannot omit the possibility of a homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s deduction is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit would have been here last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About Gamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he directed a complaint to a bread company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Regarding the Nico-nico Red Bean Bread\Nmanufactured by our company..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We have received your constructive\Ncriticism from your call just days ago."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:12:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he did file a complaint with that bread company,\Nit couldn't be considered a useful motive for murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, to what extent will you insist this is a homicide!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until it makes sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know my uncle killed himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I can't be sure of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you have been having quarrels with Gamou-shi recently, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't that big of a deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You tried to borrow money from him,\Nbut he refused without even blinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've heard that you've seen through a suicide\Nthat was actually a murder case, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you already know who the culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not so fast—even someone of my caliber couldn't be that quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:56.08,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(290,0)}Yamane Yasushi (30)\NTouyou Sports Reporter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:56.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,But isn't it a shift in responsibility for you to\Ninsist that a suicide is actually a murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He requested of you to find his alibi witness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet you found no one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And disappointed your client.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd you hear such a thing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure that's our primary concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy—how did he know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt the police would tell him that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just how will you take responsibility for your client's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gamou-shi did not commit suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a homicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will absolutely seek out the perpetrator!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,Detective Mouri Kogoro\N"I will absolutely seek out the perpetrator!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Fabulous Job!\NMouri Kogorou does it again!\N"Leave it to me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.54,Signs,,0,0,0,,Pathetic! Running Away\Nfrom Responsibility\NMouri Kogoro Leads His Client to Death\NThe "Famous Detective," just a glory of the past···?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad's the hero of the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, just get back together already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go tell him that if he pushes his luck too much, he'll fall into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll get many, many clients at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before that, please allow me to watch some horse-racing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom's probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rider has fallen from his horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now, the first ones to cross the finish\Nline: Ooana, number 4, and number 18!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Ooana won!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won, I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just ran into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takeoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:49.49,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Takeoka Isao (40)\NFormer Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've grown so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The detective who falsely arrested Gamou-shi five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And left the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he said "gift," he had to mean this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Animal cookies...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Takeoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This can't be suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not Gamou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I questioned him five years ago and know he isn't the suicidal type.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be like you to do nothing when one\Nof your clients was killed by someone, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think his death might involve a grudge or a conflict of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're thinking grudges, I know one suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a major grudge, but I did have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It counts as a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you the night before yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the estimated time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around 9:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I met up with a friend at 8:30, and we stayed together until midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So his alibi's as firm as steel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go, Takeoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's over—your commitment to your previous client.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing's over yet; nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're investigating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Gamou being out of the way still isn't enough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What've you been doing these past five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not a peep from you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Consider me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective work was what I did best, but I threw that away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's still the career path of private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could be one in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was with the central police and he was with district.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite the difference, we teamed up\Nnumerous times during our investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that some clients have held unreasonable grudges against us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the owner, Gamou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:04.91,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Tsuchida Reiji (43)\NHaraiso Finance Co. CEO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:04.91,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Already made me CEO and left all responsibility to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So was he hated outside of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not familiar with his private matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about asking his nephew?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the only one that's related to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to make me the culprit by force?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're just trying to confirm something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The night before yesterday, I was drawing an illustration\Nfor a serial novel that runs in a weekly magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, any witnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been borrowing money here and there, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've obtained some interesting information from a nearby bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After getting yourself drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You grumbled over your drink, saying, "If only uncle\Nwere dead, I could have that inheritance right now."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I was just drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I'll say this one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number of culprits that have successfully escaped\Nfrom me, the famous detective, Mouri Kogoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amount to absolutely zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were no results in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, only for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, about that Arai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he'd like this to be a suicide case no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There'll be a full-blow investigation if this is deemed a homicide case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't want his dirty little secrets to be discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Takeoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've thought of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no reason I'd tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why should I tell you who it was that\Ntold me Gamou-shi had hired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you won't leak your news source, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it weren't from the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could only come from his nephew, Arai Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you already knew that, you didn't have to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Print an apology for this stupid report!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it was just as you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arai was the one who told the reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he would get the entire inheritance...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there were zero witnesses to the alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention using the media to throw you off...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make him spit everything out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death for Arai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happens to be around 9:00 and 10:00 last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:19:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe this is the best evidence indicating he had killed Gamou-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, this is the neighbor living next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said that, on the night Gamou-shi died...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he was so noisy, I thought about complaining to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I looked over to his room from the veranda...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And saw him walking to and fro, shouting something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he soon went quiet, so I didn't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little before 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,8:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get to that forest from here, it would take an hour and a half by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he were in his room at 8:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how much he hurried, he couldn't\Nmake it in time for Gamou-shi's time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Arai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means there was only one reason he would commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was innocent but I suspected him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By pressuring him, I caused his death...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like you brought us some serious\Ntrouble with your suspicions, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No excuses from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I was the one who insisted on\Ninviting Mouri to find the real culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will take responsibility for this incident my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As usual, lots of them have shown up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was glad to team up with you again, like the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll see you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you not falsely accuse Arai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to prove his innocence, he took his\Nown life to detest you, isn't that right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How will you answer to that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You made an innocent person die, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Arai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} really commit...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, this is Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Starting today...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Close up my detective agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giving up his practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's giving up being a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.57,0:23:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reconsider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:23:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It all began with this request...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm a detective to the bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.78,0:24:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.11,0:24:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Voice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.11,0:24:36.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Is Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} giving up being a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:38.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Then, who's going to solve the cases!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.83,0:24:40.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
